{"tid":2004743,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"幾時變有不反先出去遊行？","createTime":"2020-05-06T15:43:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-07T07:50:31.000Z","uid":13936,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a028ea16809efb5055adedcd9a26a7251b4177d7","tid":2004743,"uid":13936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T15:43:34.000Z","msg":"唔批不反 預料之中<br />\n搞手點都要講延期<br />\n如果唔係搞手就會比狗咬 <br />\n<br />\n香城online玩左咁耐<br />\n有無不反咪一鳩樣<br />\n1月19號個天下制裁集會有不反呀<br />\n結果？<br />\n睇下琴日嘅新聞<br />\n現場被捕嘅手足加控暴動呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有撚分別呀？<br />\n<br />\n反正宜家就實有人會出<br />\n人多手足安全嘅機會先大啲<br />\n你唔出 佢唔出<br />\n出左嘅手足又會被人屌送頭<br />\n<br />\n到時人少咪去海港城行下街<br />\n夜晚再去朗豪坊涼下冷氣囉<br />\n呢啲先叫be water"},{"pid":"ed521e0bfa56ccfc6ef1b47e3765f3ef619a9782","tid":2004743,"uid":13936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T15:51:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"61427a64b448ae937dafaae134cc74c0d9d8f9db","tid":2004743,"uid":13936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T15:54:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"64737c0e603d920ea17fb744741bf128881fd88b","tid":2004743,"uid":222071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T16:03:48.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"14c00f9ccd3513722b3b835ab594c21ee3195b5d","tid":2004743,"uid":13936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T16:06:09.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"795ad76068737fd385b30a12db54163838744112","tid":2004743,"uid":13936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T16:13:49.000Z","msg":"手足歸隊"},{"pid":"8c57b8e074d4066e36eee3565b8f6ed442030916","tid":2004743,"uid":13936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T16:13:59.000Z","msg":"星"},{"pid":"848ef0cd732e47803005f9621fba2b26f